        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;World Language Education Assistance Program Act or the World LEAP Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Education to award competitive grants to local educational agencies to establish and carry out new, or improve existing, world language or dual language programs.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
